data.description: New pictures added!! Absolutely stunning 4 Bed, 3 FULL Baths with a deep extended 2 car garage situated in an award winning 55+ Community. Spacious great room with vaulted ceilings with a cozy electric fireplace. Very bright and open large eat-in-kitchen with stainless steel appliances and a gorgeous island with seating. A full bathroom for guests is on the first floor as well as a nice size office/flex room. Huge first floor master bedroom with its own private full bath! First floor laundry with newer washer and dryer that stays! Main floor has two more great size bedrooms! Stunning fully finished lower level with a FULL KITCHEN. Also includes a huge bedroom with another full nice size bathroom. Great for entertaining guests! Gorgeous backyard includes composite decking with adjustable pergola, and with retractable awning, stamped ground patio and a gas grill! Other great features this home offers is permanent security system with live view camera system and ADT monitoring, hardwired CO and smoke detectors, yard lights, and irrigation system, The HOA includes grass cutting, mulch, snow removal, pruning and weed and feed, assessments reserve, community center, and insurance. The Hot Tub and the Electric Fireplace will stay!
